Package: dissertation
Version: 0.0-0.1
Date: 2026-4-1
Title: An AI-Native Dissertation Framework Built on R Package Architecture
Description: A forkable framework for writing an AI-native dissertation that treats
    AI as a collaborator in analysis, writing, and dissemination. The package unifies
    Quarto (.qmd) source files, reproducible statistical analyses, machine-readable APIs,
    and MCP (Model Context Protocol) endpoints. It compiles a thesis-ready PDF via
    institutional thesis.cls and publishes an interactive website with a chatbot that
    lets readers explore methods, results, and code. Designed as a template for graduate
    students, advisors, and methodologists in educational measurement and adjacent fields.
